Introduction

PRECIOUS was a five-member girl group under UMI Entertainment. They debuted on September 23, 2020 with the digital single album "Let It Shine!". On September 23, 2022, it was announced that the contracts of members JiHyo, LeeSoo, and HanByeol had been terminated. MinJeong, HeeSu, and HyoJin joined the group in April 2023.

On February 17, 2024, Han Woom announced on Pocketdols that the group had disbanded and that the members would go on separate paths.
